gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.ui.common
Class ContextFileManager

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.ui.common.ContextFileManager

public class ContextFileManager
extends java.lang.Object

This class defines a list of functions to facilitate the management and synchronization of files that may be simultaneously accessed across different context client, such as an SCM file being used at SCM and Map panel.

Since:
CMTS v1.0
